'''人體增强'''（{{lang-en|Human enhancement}}）是指那些希望通过自然或人工的手段暂时或永久的克服现在[[人体|人体]]局限的尝试。这个术语有时适用于使用技术手段选择或改变人类的素质和能力，而不管这些改变是否超越现在人类的极限。现在的考验是，这种技术是否用于非[[治疗|治疗]]的目的。一些[[倫理學|伦理学家]]将该术语限定为为了非治疗目的在[[人类生物学|人类生物学]]上使用特定技术——包括[[神经学|神经学]]、[[计算机|计算机]]、[[基因治疗|基因治疗]]以及[[纳米技术|纳米技术]]。<ref name="Hughes 2004 (paper)">{{cite journal| author = Hughes, James| title = Human Enhancement on the Agenda| year = 2004| url = http://ieet.org/index.php/IEET/more/human_enhancement_on_the_agenda/| accessdate = 2007-02-02| archive-date = 2013-01-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130113012223/http://ieet.org/index.php/IEET/more/human_enhancement_on_the_agenda| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>Moore, P., "Enhancing Me: The Hope and the Hype of Human Enhancement", John Wiley, 2008</ref>

==技术== 
人类增强技术不仅是为了治疗[[疾病|疾病]]和[[残疾|残疾]]，而且也为了增强人类素质。<ref name="Enhancement Technologies Group 1998">{{cite journal|    author = Enhancement Technologies Group|    title = Writings by group participants|    year = 1998|    url = http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~ucbtdag/bioethics/writings/index.html|    accessdate = 2007-02-02|    archive-date = 2018-02-28|    archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180228024729/http://www.ucl.ac.uk/~ucbtdag/bioethics/writings/index.html|    dead-url = no}}</ref>某些学术圈子中，人类增强技术意味着[[新兴技术|新兴技术]]和[[技术融合|会聚技术]]。<ref name="Roco and Bainbridge 2004"/>另一些时候它与[[人类遗传工程|人类遗传工程]]大致同义，<ref name="Agar 2004">{{cite book|author = Agar, Nicholas|title = Liberal Eugenics: In Defence of Human Enhancement|year = 2004|isbn = 1-4051-2390-7}}</ref><ref name="Parens 2000">{{cite book| author = Parens, Erik| title = Enhancing Human Traits: Ethical and Social Implications| publisher = Georgetown University Press| year = 2000| isbn = 0-87840-780-4}}</ref>更通常的，它是指综合运用纳米技术、[[生物技术|生物技术]]、[[信息技术|信息技术]]和[[认知科学|认知科学]]来改善人类的功效。<ref name="Roco and Bainbridge 2004">{{cite book| author = Roco, Mihail C. and Bainbridge, William Sims, eds.| title = Converging Technologies for Improving Human Performance| publisher = Springer| year = 2004| isbn = 1402012543}}</ref>

